<p><a href="https://enchantedlion.com/all-books/at-the-drop-of-a-cat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=680%2C406&#038;ssl=1" alt width="680" height="406" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81327 jetpack-lazy-image" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=320%2C191&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=600%2C358&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=240%2C143&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=768%2C458&amp;ssl=1 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=680%2C406&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img data-lazy-fallback="1" decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=680%2C406&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="406" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81327" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=320%2C191&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=600%2C358&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=240%2C143&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat3.jpg?resize=768%2C458&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-recalc-dims="1"  /></noscript></a></p>
<p><a href="https://enchantedlion.com/all-books/at-the-drop-of-a-cat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=680%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt width="680" height="469" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81326 jetpack-lazy-image" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=320%2C221&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=600%2C414&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=240%2C166&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=768%2C530&amp;ssl=1 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=680%2C469&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img data-lazy-fallback="1" decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=680%2C469&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="469" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81326" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=320%2C221&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=600%2C414&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=240%2C166&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat4.jpg?resize=768%2C530&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-recalc-dims="1"  /></noscript></a></p>
<p>The day comes when the child reads a poem to his grandfather &#8212; he has finally learned to read and write, but he has also learned something else: that there are many languages of connection, each with its own dignity and delight, each an outstretched hand reaching for another.</p>
<p><a href="https://enchantedlion.com/all-books/at-the-drop-of-a-cat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=680%2C939&#038;ssl=1" alt width="680" height="939" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81324 jetpack-lazy-image" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=320%2C442&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=600%2C829&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=240%2C331&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=768%2C1060&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=1112%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1112w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=680%2C939&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img data-lazy-fallback="1" decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=680%2C939&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="939" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81324" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=320%2C442&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=600%2C829&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=240%2C331&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=768%2C1060&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat6.jpg?resize=1112%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1112w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-recalc-dims="1"  /></noscript></a></p>
<p><a href="https://enchantedlion.com/all-books/at-the-drop-of-a-cat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=680%2C432&#038;ssl=1" alt width="680" height="432" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81334 jetpack-lazy-image" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=320%2C203&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=600%2C381&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=240%2C152&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=768%2C488&amp;ssl=1 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-lazy-src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=680%2C432&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img data-lazy-fallback="1" decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=680%2C432&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="680" height="432" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-81334" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=320%2C203&amp;ssl=1 320w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=600%2C381&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=240%2C152&amp;ssl=1 240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.themarginalian.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/atthedropofacat20.jpg?resize=768%2C488&amp;ssl=1 768w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" data-recalc-dims="1"  /></noscript></a></p>
<p>Couple <a href="https://enchantedlion.com/all-books/at-the-drop-of-a-cat" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong><em>At the Drop of a Cat</em></strong></a> with <a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2022/01/16/what-is-love-carson-ellis-mac-barnett/"><em>What Is Love?</em></a> &#8212; a kindred reckoning with the consolations of connection, told through the tender relationship between a child and a grandparent &#8212; then revisit <a href="https://www.themarginalian.org/2018/10/09/the-forest-riccardo-bozzi/"><em>The Forest</em></a> &#8212; a love letter to our bond with the wilderness, also illustrated by Violeta Lópiz.</p>
		</div>

			</div><!--END posts-->

